0.25872}]],"source":"hejfish_api_map_geojson","confidence":"high"},"links":{"source":"https://www.hejfish.com/d/13121-hoern-am-postsee","hejfish":"https://www.hejfish.com/d/13121-hoern-am-postsee","alleangeln":null,"website":null,"image":"https://file.hejfish.com/image/cc1200x900/74/61/74619987b0b49622b640987dc6dd9881d17a56f5.jpeg"},"fish":["Flussbarsch","Hecht","Zander","Aal","Div. Weißfische"],"metadata":{"platform":"hejfish","geocode_source":"hejfish_api_map_geojson","slug":"hoern-am-postsee","seo_name":"Hörn am Postsee","description":"<p><b>die Hörn am Postsee</b></p> <p>Die Hörn ist ein Teil des Postsee (ca. 130 ha). In diesem Gewässer fängt man im Herbst hervorragend große Barsche. Hechte sind auch sehr zahlreich vertreten, Zander kommen eher sehr selten vor. Neben den üblichen Weißfischen kann man aber auch Aale als frischen Fang mit nach Hause nehmen.</p> <p><b>Barrierefreier Angelplatz! (54.244001, 10.268888)<br></b>Weitere Informationen finden Sie hier: <a href=\"http://www.barrierefreies-angeln-sh.de/seite/573983/postsee-preetz.html\">Klick</a></p> <p>Weitere barrierefreie Angelplätze finden Sie hier: <a href=\"https://www.hejfish.com/search?term=barrierefrei\">Klick</a><br></p>","borders":"<p>Gewässer-Grenzen entnehmen Sie dem PDF.</p>\n\n<p>Geo-Daten: <br>Parkmöglichkeit / Zugang Wanderweg    54.244320, 10.269572</p>\n\n<p>Besonderheit:  <br>Barrierefreie Angelplattform         54.244001, 10.268888 <br><br><br></p>","techniques":["Ansitzangeln","Feedern","Friedfischangeln","Karpfenangeln","Posenangeln","Raubfischangeln","Spinnangeln"],"rules_text":"<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 11.25pt 0cm 0.0001pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Angelbedingungen</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 18pt;\"><span tahoma\",sans-serif;=\"\" mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:black;mso-fareast-language:=\"\" de\"=\"\" style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">Neben den gesetzlichen Bedingungen gelten noch weitere nachfolgend aufgeführte:</span></p><ul type=\"disc\" style=\"margin-top: 0cm;\"><li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span tahoma\",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:=\"\" \"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";mso-fareast-language:de\"=\"\" style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">max. 3 Angeln vom Ufer bzw. einem Ruderboot mit ASV-Kennzeichen. Je Angel 1 Haken</span></li><li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span tahoma\",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:=\"\" \"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";mso-fareast-language:de\"=\"\" style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">Mindestmaße: Aal 50 cm, Hecht 60 cm&nbsp;ansonsten die gesetzlichen Mindestmaße gemäß Binnenfischereiverordnung des Landes Schleswig-Holstein (BiFVo, aktuellste Fassung vom 05.08.2021),&nbsp;</span><span tahoma\",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:=\"\" \"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:black;mso-fareast-language:de\"=\"\" style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">gekennzeichnete Fische sind umgehend beim Gewässerwart zu melden</span></li><li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span tahoma\",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:=\"\" \"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";mso-fareast-language:de\"=\"\" style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">untermäßige Fische sind sofort frei zu lassen</span></li><li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span tahoma\",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:=\"\" \"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";mso-fareast-language:de\"=\"\" style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">Schonzeiten nach der gültigen BiFVo (gemäß Gesetz), der Hecht ist auch bis zum 30.04. geschont</span></li><li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span tahoma\",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:=\"\" \"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";mso-fareast-language:de\"=\"\" style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">die Verwendung lebender Köderfische ist verboten,</span></li><li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span tahoma\",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:=\"\" \"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";mso-fareast-language:de\"=\"\" style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">die Köderfische müssen aus dem Gewässer stammen,</span></li><li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span tahoma\",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:=\"\" \"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";mso-fareast-language:de\"=\"\" style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">der Angelplatz bzw. das Ruderboot sind selbstverständlich immer sauber zu verlassen!</span></li><li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span tahoma\",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:=\"\" \"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";mso-fareast-language:de\"=\"\" style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">vom Ufer der Gewässer Lanker See, Kirchsee, Schwentine und&nbsp;</span><span tahoma\",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:=\"\" \"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:black;mso-fareast-language:de\"=\"\" style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">an der Hörn des Postsee darf geangelt werden</span></li><li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span tahoma\",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:=\"\" \"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";mso-fareast-language:de\"=\"\" style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">Inseln dürfen&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 700;\"><u>nicht</u></span>&nbsp;betreten oder mit dem Boot angefahren werden,</span></li><li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span tahoma\",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:=\"\" \"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";mso-fareast-language:de\"=\"\" style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">Uferbewuchs darf nicht beschädigt werden, vom Reet ist Abstand zu halten,</span></li><li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span tahoma\",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:=\"\" \"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";mso-fareast-language:de\"=\"\" style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">das Aufstellen von Zelten, sowie das Campen an den Gewässern ist untersagt, &nbsp;</span></li><li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span tahoma\",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:=\"\" \"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";mso-fareast-language:de\"=\"\" style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">offenes Feuer ist an den Uferkanten verboten,</span></li><li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span tahoma\",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:=\"\" \"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";mso-fareast-language:de\"=\"\" style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">Hunde sind immer an der Leine zu führen,</span></li><li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span tahoma\",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:=\"\" \"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";mso-fareast-language:de\"=\"\" style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">der Gastangler haftet für alle durch ihn entstandenen Schäden,</span><span tahoma\",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:=\"\" \"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:black;mso-fareast-language:de\"=\"\" style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">&nbsp;der ASV Preetz und Umgebung e.V. ist von jeglicher Haftung befreit.</span></li></ul><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; background-image: none; background-position: 0% 0%; background-size: initial; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: normal;\"><span tahoma\",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:=\"\" \"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:black;mso-fareast-language:de\"=\"\" style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><u><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Besondere Bestimmungen:</span></u><br></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; background-image: none; background-position: 0% 0%; background-size: initial; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: normal;\"><span tahoma\",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:=\"\" \"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:black;mso-fareast-language:de\"=\"\" style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">Private Boote, Kajaks, Tretboote, Paddelboote, Faltboote, Schlauchboote etc. dürfen nicht zum Angeln verwendet werden.&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; background-image: none; background-position: 0% 0%; background-size: initial; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: normal;\"><span tahoma\",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:=\"\" \"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:black;mso-fareast-language:de\"=\"\" style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; background-image: none; background-position: 0% 0%; background-size: initial; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.3333px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Alle Arten von Motoren an den Ruderbooten sind verboten!</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; background-image: none; background-position: 0% 0%; background-size: initial; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: normal;\"><span tahoma\",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:=\"\" \"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:black;mso-fareast-language:de\"=\"\" style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><br></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; background-image: none; background-position: 0% 0%; background-size: initial; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: normal;\"><span tahoma\",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:=\"\" \"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:black;mso-fareast-language:de\"=\"\" style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">Die Freudenholmer Bucht steht unseren Gästen derzeit NICHT zur Verfügung und darf NICHT beangelt oder befahren werden!&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; background-image: none; background-position: 0% 0%; background-size: initial; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: normal;\"><span tahoma\",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:=\"\" \"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:black;mso-fareast-language:de\"=\"\" style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><br></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; background-image: none; background-position: 0% 0%; background-size: initial; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: normal;\"><span tahoma\",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:=\"\" \"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:black;mso-fareast-language:de\"=\"\" style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Sehr wichtig: Die Fangmeldung, auch wenn nichts gefangen wurde, muss online abgegeben werden. Anderenfalls erfolgt eine Ausgabe-Sperre!</span><br></span></p>","rules_files":[{"id":668266,"name":"kombi-tageskarte-fuer-die-gewaesser-lanker-see-kirchsee-hoern-am-postsee-und-schwentine-bestimmungen","description":null,"file":"https://api.hejfish.com/files/download/a2f10c00618468aad53a09023c3ec1bd2a0873b6/kombi-tageskarte-fuer-die-gewaesser-lanker-see-kirchsee-hoern-am-postsee-und-schwentine-bestimmungen.pdf"},{"id":668267,"name":"kombi-24-stundenkarte-fuer-die-gewaesser-lanker-see-kirchsee-hoern-am-postsee-und-schwentine-bestimmungen","description":null,"file":"https://api.hejfish.com/files/download/3bfc81bd69aa8735efa5d8f87d584231d1294351/kombi-24-stundenkarte-fuer-die-gewaesser-lanker-see-kirchsee-hoern-am-postsee-und-schwentine-bestimmungen.pdf"},{"id":668265,"name":"kombi-wochenendkarte-fuer-die-gewaesser-lanker-see-kirchsee-hoern-am-postsee-und-schwentine-bestimmungen","description":null,"file":"https://api.hejfish.com/files/download/37c445aaf7f137ee8f67c4f7be99ce5d5cfc2776/kombi-wochenendkarte-fuer-die-gewaesser-lanker-see-kirchsee-hoern-am-postsee-und-schwentine-bestimmungen.pdf"},{"id":668264,"name":"kombi-wochenkarte-fuer-die-gewaesser-lanker-see-kirchsee-hoern-am-postsee-und-schwentine-bestimmungen","description":null,"file":"https://api.hejfish.com/files/download/eb15a61ec953ad18330ee992a6e46261110c5c7b/kombi-wochenkarte-fuer-die-gewaesser-lanker-see-kirchsee-hoern-am-postsee-und-schwentine-bestimmungen.pdf"},{"id":193312,"name":"tageskarte-bestimmungen","description":null,"file":"https://api.hejfish.com/files/download/3690dc41e33388e2ce2c5658a55ac79d0c4c85e5/tageskarte-bestimmungen.pdf"},{"id":193311,"name":"24-stundenkarte-bestimmungen","description":null,"file":"https://api.hejfish.com/files/download/de132c9bd780ad39f5eb7bb0423145285d368913/24-stundenkarte-bestimmungen.pdf"},{"id":668272,"name":"kombi-tageskarte-mit-bootskarte-ohne-boot-fuer-die-gewaesser-lanker-see-kirchsee-h